\mt1 2 TESALONAIKA  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Wan pas wun Pol p…®l…®wukna pasa. Sailas, Timoti wunogwinala l…®gamb…®t. Tesalonaikamba yisola la n…®na nyaek Godna mbaapma n…®mba kat p…®l…®wut…®na pasa. N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistna mbaapma n…®mba ngwuk.  
\v 2 N…®na nyaek God n…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist awagapma kwil…®mba vak klangwangat wan…®n. Apma maawut s…®ka yet…®ngweya vak klangwangat wan…®n.   
\s1 POL GOD KAT S∆óVU K∆óL∆óGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 3 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba, awat sowat woviyaguga l…®ngwa vat n…®man yil…®gand…®. God waa nyaang…®t kwutaa l…®ngwa vat n…®man yil…®gand…®. Kwutaa l…®ngwa vat v…®laa God kat ngwuk kat t…®ga nj…®mbla nj…®mbla s…®vu k…®l…®gan…®n. S…®vu k…®l…®na vat nglaatnd…®.  
\v 4 Ngi kat t…®ga God kat yelav…®pmak kat yisola la n…®mba kat kwutaa l…®ngwa vak kat t…®ga mbut…®gan…®n. Ngwutna s…® kwusol…®gan…®n. Nat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba ndi kat kavle vat yil…®ngandi. Ndi vaaka kwutaa l…®nja vak apma vak ana kwagalandi. Ndi ndina maawutmba n…®mamba kwutaa l…®gandi waa ndi kat mbut…®gan…®n.   
\s1 NGWUK KAT YIL∆óNJA KAVLE VAK KAT GOD ANA KEMAT∆óGAND∆ó  
\p
\v 5 Ngwuk kat yil…®nja kavle vak kat God ana kemat…®gand…®. Wan ngwuk kat yinjeya n…®ma vak ngwuk kat kwunakiyand…® waa God yelav…®t…®gand…®. Wan kavle vat ngwuk kat kwunatnd…® maa nd…®na mbaapmamba wuleilaa apma vat n…®nogwi l…®giyangwuk. Wan kavle vat ngwuk kat kwunatnd…® maa God t…®ga vla t…®giyangwuk.  
\v 6 Ngwuk kat n…®ma vat yil…®ga n…®mba kat ng…®ni God awat ndi kat n…®ma vat yigiyand…®. Ndi kat n…®ma vat yiweyan nlaakiyand…® waa wand…® God.  
\v 7-8 Njambwi nyan Jisas yaiga nj…®mblamba nd…®na njambwi enselonala yaigand…®. Ya vla v…®ka yaigand…®. God kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba kat yandeya nj…®mbla awat ndi kat kai waga s…®giyand…®. N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas kat wanja apma nyaang…®k kat kai wal…®ga n…®mba kat yandeya nj…®mbla awat ndi kat kai waga s…®giyand…®. Mbambala ngwuk kat n…®ma vapmba yil…®gandi. yandeya nj…®mbla ngwuk kat yat njawiya ngwula waa waigand…®. N…®no n…®n kat wupma waigand…®.  
\v 9 Wan kavle n…®mba ndi kat s…®nd…® mala nj…®mbla nj…®mbla kavle savle yet…®giyandi. God t…®ga kavamba ana l…®giyandi. Ndi kat k…®kligiyand…®. kapma kavamba yiga l…®giyandi. Wan kavamba l…®ga God kwondumba apma vat t…®ndeya vat ana v…®ga l…®giyandi.  
\v 10 Ngwuk kat wan apma nyaang…®t mbutn…®n maa wutaa ngwula maawupmba kwutaa l…®ngwuk. Jisas yaiga nj…®mbla nd…®nai waa nyaang…®t maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ngwa vak nd…®na s…® kwusogiyand…®. M…®nagwi nd…®na mbaapmamba l…®ga nat n…®mba nd…® kat v…®laa apma nglei nj…®vwa kwutnd…® waa waigangwuk.  
\v 11-12 Apma vapmba yet…®njangat ndi kat kwunap m…®la waa God kat nj…®mbla nj…®mbla wagalal…®gan…®n. Ngwutna maawupmba apma vat yet…®vak wangwa vak God ngwuk kat kwondu kwind…® maa kwukngwangat wan…®n. God kat ngwula maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ga kwukweya apma nj…®vwa God ngwuk kat kwondu kwind…® maa kwukngwangat wan…®n.   
\c 2  
\s1 GOD WAA LO KAT KAI WAL∆óGA NYAN  
\p
\v 1-2 N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist yaiga nj…®mbla ngwuk kat mbupmak yigan…®n. Nd…®nai l…®ga kavamba yisolaa l…®neya vak kat ngwuk kat mbupmat yigan…®n. K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba, nat n…®mba ngwuk kat mbut…®ndi. Njambwi nyan yaiga nj…®mbla tamba yand…® waa mbutndi. Nat n…®mba kwo waa kwudimba mbutndi. Nat n…®mba Godna waagan wuna maawupmba ngwand…®nd…® mala mbut…®gowun waa wan nyaang…®t mbutndi. Nat n…®mba pas n…®na s…®mba waga p…®l…®wutaa wan nyaang…®t ngwuk kat kwindi. Ndinai waa nyaang…®t ke ngwut n…®mamba yelav…®ka. Mand…®t maawut ke yelav…®ka.  
\v 3 Ngwuk kat woseka walandi. Nat nda tata yand…® mala wan nandinya ng…®ni yaigand…®. Tat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisola l…®ga God kat kai wavat n…®ma sakwat n…®mba yisola l…®ga God kat kai wavat laataa yaigandi. Tata God kat kavle vat yil…®ga nyan laataa l…®giyand…®. Nd…® ya v…®t…®ga kava yilaa n…®mamba kavle yigiyand…®.  
\v 4 Nd…® waigand…®. Nat vat n…®ma nda kat yelav…®kngwa vat kwaga ngwula. Wun ndi kat kwulat…®gowun. Wun kat m…®na yelav…®ka al…® ngwula waa waigand…®. Godna ngay wuleilaa ndaal…®ga wun God wun waa waigand…®.  
\v 5 Tamba ngwulogwinala l…®ga wan nyaang…®t mbukwun ngwuk kat. Ngwuk yelav…®t…®gangwuk?  
\v 6 Mbambala k…®ta vatna nd…® kat kemat…®ga. Kemat…®ga nda v…®ga l…®gangwuk. Wan nda kemat…® mala nd…® kan nj…®mbla ana laakiyand…®. Wandeya nj…®mblamba laakiyand…®.  
\v 7 Wan kavle nyan kavle vat yindeya vak kan nj…®mba wan vak pagwuga yil…®gandi. Wan kavle nyan kat kemat…®ga nda ng…®ni ana kemakiyand…®.  
\v 8 Wan kavle nyan kat kematapman yindeya ng…®ni laataa kapmba l…®giyand…®. N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist ngaga yalaa wan kavle nyan kat kai waa nd…® kat vatnyagiyand…®. Njambwi nyan n…®ma ya v…®t…®ga vak vla yandeya vak wan kavle nyan v…®giyand…®. V…®nd…® maa kwundi mwupmba ya v…®l…®k puvwinda vak vla wan kavle nyan kat Jisas vatnyagiyand…®.  
\v 9 Wan kavle nyan setena kwondumba yalaa n…®ma vat yil…®nja vak woseka waa s…®mogwigiyand…®. Yindeya n…®ma vak vilaa waigandi. Nd…® apma nyana kwondu wogwul…®ga nyana waa waigandi.  
\v 10 Ndi kat woseka wand…® maa ndina maawut kavle yigiyand…®. Wan n…®mba god waa apma nyaang…®ik kat kai waigandi. Kai wanjangat God ndi kat ana kwunakiyand…®. Wan n…®mba wan kavle nyan woseka waa yil…®nda vat v…®laa maawupmba yelav…®ka l…®giyandi. T…®ga l…®ga kavle vat yigiyandi.  
\v 11 God ndi kat kavle maawut yelav…®ka yet…®njeya maawut kwigiyand…®. Ndina kavle maawupmba kavle nyan woseka waiga nyaang…®tg kwutaa l…®giyandi.  
\v 12 God waa apma nyaang…®t ndi kwutaa l…®vak kat kai waigandi. Ndi kavle vapmba yet…®vat woviyaguga l…®giyandi. God wungi kavle vapmba yet…®l…®ga n…®mba kat aywaa kimbut yiga lindeya maawupmba si…®giyand…® ndi kat.   
\s1 TAMBA GOD NGWUK KAT KWUNAPMAK WAND∆ó  
\p
\v 13 Ngwuk kapma vapmba l…®ga n…®mba ngwuk. K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba, njambwi nyan ngwuk kat woviyaguga l…®gand…®. Tamba ngwuk kat yelav…®taa kwunakiyowun waa wand…® ngwuk kat. Wunai waa apma nyaang…®t ndi kwutaa l…®giyandi. Ndi kat wuna waagan kwigiyowun. Wuna waagan tavind…® maa apma mand…®t maawupmba yet…®giyandi. Ndi kat apma vapmba yigand…® waa tamba God wand…® ngwuk kat. Ngi kat t…®ga God kat ngwuk kat t…®ga s…®vu k…®neyan nglaatnd…®.  
\v 14 God wand…®, ngwuk kat wan apma nyaang…®t mbut…®n…®n. n…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist apma vak t…®nda vla t…®ngwangat God n…®n kat ambuk, waa wand…® maa ngwuk kat mbut…®gan…®n.  
\v 15 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba wan n…®na kwundimba ngambun…®n, wukngwa nyaang…®t pasmba p…®l…®wutna nyaang…®t ke kwagalaga. Ngwula maawupmba kwutaa yet…® ngwula.  
\v 16 N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistno n…®na nyaek Godno n…®n kat woviyaguga l…®gamb…®t. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla apma vat t…®neya vat n…®n kat awagapma kwimb…®t. Apma vat n…®n kat yimbeya vak kat yelav…®ka kawiga l…®gan…®n.  
\v 17 Ngwula maawut kwunapmbangat wagalan…®n. Ngwuk kat kwondu kwimb…®t maa apma nj…®vwa kwuka apma nyaang…®t mbukngwangat mb…®k kat wagalaa l…®gan…®n.   
\c 3  
\s1 N∆óN KAT T∆óGA GOD KAT WAGALA NGWULA  
\p
\v 1 N…®n mbaapma n…®mba, ngwuk kat mbut…®na nyaang…®tna ngt…®ni la l…®ga nyaang…®t k…®ngiyan ngwuk kat mbutna. N…®n kat t…®ga God kat wagala ngwula. Ngepma ngepmamba l…®ga kwiyatapman mbutseli mbutsela mbutnjangat wagala ngwula. Wan apma nyaang…®t ndi kat kwulatndangat wagala ngwula. Ngwuk kat mbutn…®n, wan apma nyaang…®t ngwuk kat kwulatnd…®, ngwula maawupmba yelav…®ka kwutaa l…®ngwuk.  
\v 2 N…®n kat kavle vat yivat wal…®ga kavle n…®mba n…®n kat mbaa kwulatandi waa wagala ngwula. Wan n…®mba n…®na mbaapmamba l…®ga n…®mba ana ndi. Ngepma ngepmamba l…®ga n…®mba n…®na mbaapmamba ana aywaa l…®gandi. Ndina nat n…®mba m…®na n…®na mbaapmamba l…®gandi.  
\v 3 Njambwi nyan waiga nyaang…®tmba yigiyand…®. Ngwuk kat ava kwind…® mala l…®giyangwuk. Ngwuk kat God t…®vwi k…®l…®nd…® mala ngwuk kat Seten ana wuleiga kavle vat yigiyand…®.  
\v 4 Njambwi nyan ngwula maawutmba ngwand…®nd…® maa ngwuk kat wana nyaang…®tmba yiga yet…®giyangwuk. Yiga yet…®ngweya vak kat n…®na mbang…® ana k…®l…®pang…® yigiyand…®. Nguwk wan vak tamba yiga yet…®l…®ngwa vatna.  
\v 5 Njambwi nyan njwula maawupmba ngwand…®la l…®nd…® maa God kat woviyaguga l…®ngwangat wan…®n. Kraist wan nyaang…®tmba ngwula maawupmba yelav…®ka n…®ma vat kwutaa l…®ngwangat wan…®n.   
\p
\v 6 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba njambwi nyan Jisas Kraistna s…®mba ngwuk kat n…®mamba mbut…®gan…®n. Ngwula k…®ta nyan nj…®vwa kwutapman kwo l…®ndeyan nd…®nagwinala ana l…®giyangwuk. Wan nyan tat ngwuk kat mbutna vapmba ana yet…®l…®gand…®.  
\v 7 Yet…®na vapmba yet…® ngwula. Ngwutnagwinala t…®ga nj…®vwa kwutapman kwo ana yet…®l…®n…®n. V…®ga l…®ngwuk.  
\v 8 Nat n…®mbana nao kwo klalaa ana k…®l…®n…®n sanya kwilapman. Ngwutnamba sanya klavak kat kai walaa nandinya ngan n…®ma nj…®vwa kwut…®n…®n. Ngwuk kat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwivak kat kai wan…®n.  
\v 9 Yet…®na vapmba yet…® ngwula waa ngwuk kat mbupmak wan…®n. Ngi kat n…®ma nj…®vwa kwivak kat kai wan…®n. Ngwutnamba tamba sanya klal…®gen…®n nglaakend…®. Yet…®na vapmba yet…® ngwula waa ngwuk kat mbupmak wan…®n. Ngi kat t…®ga ngwutnamba sanya ana klan…®n.  
\v 10 Ngwulogwinana l…®ga wan nyaang…®t ngwuk kat mbutn…®n. K…®ta nyan nd…® nj…®vwa kwupmak kat kai wandeyan nd…® kat nao ke kwiga.  
\v 11 Ngwutno nat n…®mba ndina nj…®vwa kwagalalaa nat n…®mbana nj…®vwa kat ndi njangumba wuka yiga v…®ndi. Yinja vak wuka l…®n…®n.  
\v 12 Njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist waa vapmba wundi nyangu kat njsvwa agwut wal…®gan…®n. Nat n…®mbana nj…®vwa kat njangumba wuka ke yil…®ngwa waa wal…®gan…®n. Ndina nj…®vwamba kwuka sanya klaigandi.  
\v 13 K…®ta mbaapma n…®mba, ngwuk apma nj…®vwa kwupmak kat ngwula mbang…® k…®l…®pang…® yiland…®.  
\v 14 K…®ta nyan wan pasmba p…®l…®wutna nyaang…®k kat kai wandeya nd…® kat yigumba av…®mba. Nd…® kat kwagala. Nd…® kat kwagalangweyan nd…®na mbang…® ngwuk kat v…®ndeyan wup yigiaynd…®.  
\v 15 Maama n…®mba kat yinja vak vla nd…® kat wupma ke yingwa. Nd…® kat ambupmbangwuk.  
\v 16 Apma vat kwil…®ga njambwi nyan ngwuk kat maawupmba apma vat kwindangat wan…®n. Nj…®mbla nj…®mbla mand…®t mand…®t vapmba kwindangat wan…®n. Njambwi nyan ngwutnogwinala k…®ta vat t…®ndangat wan…®n.   
\p
\v 17 Wun Pol wun ngwuk kat apma nandinya waa p…®l…®wupmak wowun. Ngi kat t…®ga wuna taambamba wan kavamba wan vandi p…®l…®wut…®gowun. P…®l…®wukwa pas aywaa p…®l…®wut…®gowun.  
\v 18 N…®na njambwi nyan Jisas Kraist n…®n kat awagapma kwinda vak klambangwuk walaa ngwuk kat wal…®gowun.   